blog.title: Yo I Comment On The Drama When Shit Hits The Fan
blog.description:
Phandom drama? It's more likely than you think.

.

My ask box is always open if you need a place to be dramatic, share theories, conspiracies, opinions, or general grievances. Fire away, my babies. Nothing is off limits. (Except for the things that are.)

.

summary: Y’know, for a blog that basically does nothing but lovingly talk shit about Dan and Phil, and their fans, I don’t get nearly as...
body:
Y’know, for a blog that basically does nothing but lovingly talk shit about Dan and Phil, and their fans, I don’t get nearly as much hate as one would expect.


Thank y’all for being rational sons of bitches.


(But also like, don’t be scared to send me opinions that conflict with my own. This ain’t no echo chamber)

summary: Title: Phil and The Leather Tramp Chapter Six  Word Count: 3010 Rating: T+ Chapter Six Preview: “I'm so proud of you.” Dan...
body:
Title: Phil and The Leather Tramp

Chapter Six

Word Count: 3010

Rating: T+

Chapter Six Preview: “I’m so proud of you.” Dan smiled cheekily as Phil approached holding out the white plastic bag containing the weed. 


“He made me smell them all and now I feel like I’m going to sneeze.”

“Oh no, you probably have a contact high now,” Dan’s eyebrows pulled together.


Phil’s eyes widened, “Can that happen? Dan, I’ve never been high before.” Phil felt queasy and held his hands out to make sure everything was still normal. 

“No, you dingus.” Dan threw his head back in laughter.


Read From The Beginning
